[3.010, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36m\u001b[48;5;234m\u001b[1m## 2. Ask about the file — file_id resolved by Praxis\r\n\u001b(B\u001b[m"]
[1.528, "o", "\u001b[38;5;247m\u001b[48;5;234mSend a Responses API request with file_id in an input_file\r\ncontent part. Praxis resolves it via OGX, extracts the text,\r\n\u001b(B\u001b[m"]
